{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act11d0_level_act11d0_04_end","storyGroup":"act11d0","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act11d0_level_act11d0_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"TW-4","storyName":"复仇之魂","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"得知安托之死而陷入焦虑的亚叶，被铃兰说服，两人开始为了寻找冬灵人相关的线索东奔西走。与此同时，灰喉等人也遭遇了武装感染者的领袖：整合运动，泥岩。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act11d0/level_act11d0_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act11d0_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["亚叶","铃兰","泥岩","卡达","断崖","灰喉","镇民"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"九尾狐活动 4下","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_storyendjp_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"text","text":"妈妈？妈妈，你要去哪里？","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"去高地？满是鲜花的高地？","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"......害了爸爸的坏人就在那里？那妈妈会惩罚他吗？","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"那惩罚他能让爸爸回来吗？","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"......不能？","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"那......那我不要妈妈去了。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"不去不行？可我不想妈妈回去乌萨斯......那里的面包太硬了，冬天很冷......","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"妈妈？","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"妈妈......","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":18},{"type":"text","text":"......妈妈再也没有回来。","id":19},{"type":"text","text":"我用妈妈留下的钱，继续在乌萨斯读书，生活。","id":20},{"type":"text","text":"一个人。","id":21},{"type":"text","text":"一个人等待了好几年。一个人生活了好几年。","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"直到凯尔希医生出现在我的面前，她说，她是研究所的所长，她来接我了。","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"那时凯尔希医生很疲惫，比现在还要疲惫，后来我才知道，她刚从某个遥远的地方回到这里，找到了我。","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"然后，我加入了罗德岛。","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"我问过凯尔希医生，妈妈去哪儿了。凯尔希医生没有说太多，她只告诉我，妈妈和爸爸一同，被埋葬在乌萨斯的深处。","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"她是我最尊敬的老师，最憧憬的领袖，她指导我，教育我，不仅在语言上，更靠着无数干员的所作所为感染着我。","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"但凯尔希医生她......她唯独没有回答我那个最简单的问题——","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"我该向什么复仇？","id":29},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":30},{"type":"dialog","id":31},{"type":"character","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_ltalley.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":34},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":35},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":36},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":37,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......小丽萨，你其实可以不用跟过来的。","id":39,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我不放心。","id":41,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这没什么......只是去那附近搜查一下，也许会有那支武装感染者队伍的痕迹。","id":43,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐......你觉得他们会是元凶吗？","id":45,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不确定——出于理性，“不确定”是当然的回答，毕竟我们没有证据。","id":47,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但考虑到城镇现在的情况，他们是最值得怀疑的对象，不是吗？","id":48,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"还有冬灵，塞弗林怎么也不肯多说，虽然不知道这意味着什么......但既然串通感染者队伍，那就是一路货色。","id":49,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这附近的山脉叫做冬灵山脉，常年被冰雪覆盖的荒芜山脉......有什么联系吗？","id":51,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......我不知道这些，我只知道，我要揪出凶手，然后从他那里得到一个答案。","id":53,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐，你从昨天开始就一直......很吓人。","id":55,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"丽萨......对不起。","id":57,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":".......不是每个人都能那么简单释然的。","id":58,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这种不辞而别已经是第二次了......至少这次，我不愿意再后悔了。","id":59,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":60},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"character","id":62},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_ltruins.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":64},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......唔。","id":67,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"出来吧，我没有敌意。","id":68,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"playsound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"0.6","id":69},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"character","id":71},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":72,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"char_328_cammou","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"我还觉得自己潜伏的技术很不错......你是怎么发现我们的？","id":75,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"嗯......直觉？大概吧......","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"你们，是谁？","id":78,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"（呜啊，总感觉这家伙很难对付啊。）","id":80,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"（那你就少说两句。）","id":82,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"我翻阅过罗德岛的一些战斗记录，你不是普通的感染者。","id":84,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......罗德岛？是这样，你们是......罗德岛的干员。","id":86,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"怎么办？要动手吗？","id":88,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"现在灰喉不在......但至少我们得拖住他的脚步！","id":90,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"character","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":93},{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","volume":"0.2","id":94},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"2","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":95},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":96},{"type":"character","name":"char_328_cammou","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"——！","id":98,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"——别紧张，别攻击他！卡达！","id":100,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"不要轻举妄动！","id":101,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"呃——！抱、抱歉！","id":103,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"唔......？一瞬间，你的瞳孔变得鲜红，这是某种应激反应吗？","id":105,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......是我吓到你了吗？抱歉，我只是想让你们知道......战斗是徒劳的。","id":106,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"如果你们是沃伦姆德的居民......你们最好离开这里，很危险。愤怒的冬灵人或是感染者遇到你们......你们凶多吉少。","id":107,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"......多谢忠告。","id":109,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"那么你为什么出现在这里？","id":110,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我只是来献一束花，之后我自会离开。","id":112,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"......你手里捧着的，只是普通的野花？","id":114,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"这里的秋天很冷，我时常做梦的......梦见这些花，这些花就像是那座雪山的孩子......冰凉凉的。","id":116,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......愿逝者安息。","id":117,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"（他真的只是来祈祷的？该不会是假装献花其实在释放什么源石技艺吧？）","id":119,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"（看不清他的表情就判断不出他是不是在说谎，但是......）","id":121,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"（......他好像真的很伤心。）","id":122,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"——？","id":124,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":125},{"type":"character","id":126},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#4","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"不许动，不要转身，举起手。","id":130,"figure":["char_367_swllow_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_328_cammou","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"灰喉姐！","id":132,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......什么时候出现的，竟然这么轻巧......","id":134,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"算了吧，罗德岛的弩手，你的弩箭奈何不了我。","id":135,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"不要动，我只是有话想问问——","id":137,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不展露力量的对话......毫无意义。","id":139,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#4","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"——顽冥不化！","id":141,"figure":["char_367_swllow_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":142},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#4","id":143},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":145},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":146},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":148},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"看，我捏住了你的箭......你伤不到我分毫。","id":151,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"他举起了一块岩石挡住了弩箭！？","id":153,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"不、不对！是源石技艺！他确实“捏住了”箭矢，用泥土！","id":155,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"——是吗。","id":157,"figure":["char_367_swllow_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......不。","id":159,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"至少......你也没有在出声警告之前就先放冷箭，我讨厌偷袭，不过你并不让人讨厌。","id":160,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"而且.....嗯，如果你刚才的第二支箭上弦了......会怎样？","id":161,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"那要取决于你是否来得及在脖颈处用源石技艺防御。","id":163,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"唔......虽然不一定来得及，但是这套护甲可是很厚实的......","id":165,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......算了，既然你无意死斗，那再好不过。","id":166,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我可以离开了吗？","id":167,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"很抱歉，好像还不行。","id":169,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......也是，唉。","id":171,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"虽然有各种各样的莱塔尼亚人加入了我们，队伍变得丰富多样......","id":172,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"但......作为弩手的你是不会看漏这个标志的。这个，过去属于感染者的标志。","id":173,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"整合运动点亮了一团野火，过去、现在、将来，它都将在大地的各个角落生生不息。","id":175,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"但是，整合运动这个词并不代表所有感染者。","id":176,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"所以，你呢？你是莱塔尼亚本地的响应者，还是背负着罪恶和阴谋，从别处逃来这里的流亡者？","id":177,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我......？唔......都算吧，从卡兹戴尔开始的漫无目的的旅途，我们一直在逃。","id":179,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......沃伦姆德已经是一团乱麻了，我不认为这和你们毫无关系。","id":181,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"的确，怎么会毫无关系呢。","id":183,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"但我......也不是整合运动，不再是了，我只是泥岩小队的队长，一个......雇佣兵？不，只是一个感染者吧。","id":184,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"（他怎么老是像在自言自语一样？那什么整合运动的思维都这么跳脱吗？）","id":186,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"（在行动队长进行交涉的时候麻烦你安静一点，如果你实在没事干，可以录像记录。）","id":188,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"（对哦！打开相机打开相机......）","id":190,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不过，说的也是啊......我是什么呢，我不再是雇佣兵了，不再是整合运动了，事到如今，我......","id":192,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":193},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......啊。","id":195,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"怎么了吗？","id":197,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"那个，施术的余波好像把花朵弄脏了......这个季节，好不容易采到的......","id":199,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"如果你有意战斗，能换个地方吗？","id":200,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"真是游刃有余的说法......不过，免了。","id":202,"figure":["char_367_swllow_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"卡达，断崖，不要放松警惕，但也不要攻击他，给他点空间。","id":204,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_328_cammou","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"呼......","id":206,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"——我明白了。","id":208,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"谢谢。","id":210,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......这场火灾，我们的干员似乎被卷进去了，我需要情报。","id":212,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"很抱歉......但我们也有四名同伴在这场火灾中丧生。","id":214,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"虽然我们对侦探之类的东西一窍不通......但我们之中有很多莱塔尼亚人。","id":215,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"他们都接受过系统的教育，比起其他国家的民众，他们是天生的术师。","id":216,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"至少......我可以断定，这是人祸，绝非意外。","id":217,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"谁下的手？","id":219,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"如果我们知道，那么这座城镇会因为那个人的死而重回平静......","id":221,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"你还知道些什么？比如，你刚才说了冬灵人？","id":223,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......你也许误会了，我无心与你为敌，也只是来祭奠同伴。","id":225,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"但也许有一天，我们会兵戈相向，我没有信任你们的......理由。也不会和你们分享太多信息。","id":226,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......原来如此，但是没关系，你的态度已经可以起到很大的帮助。","id":228,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"对了，你去过镇里了？","id":230,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"是。","id":232,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"怎么样了？","id":234,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"一片混乱，感染者们起来抗议，与非感染者们发生冲突。","id":236,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"是你的人在教唆他们。","id":237,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......这很不好，很多无辜的人因此受罪......但......","id":239,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......但在沃伦姆德认罪之前，在他们把凶手交出来之前，没有人会让步。","id":240,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我要用什么理由阻止那些因为同伴的枉死而愤怒的感染者......？","id":241,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"——听上去，事情并非全部在你掌握。","id":243,"figure":["char_367_swllow_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"嗯......越来越多的人被裹挟进去，迟早，我们也会......","id":245,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......我们的身份不便于走动，但是你们可以。","id":246,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"啊......我们已经说了够多了，我并不能完全信任你们，罗德岛。","id":247,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"嗯，不能够信任，那么就这样吧......再会。","id":248,"figure":["avg_npc_011",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":249},{"type":"character","id":250},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":251},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":252},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......","id":254,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"灰喉姐！那个家伙好可怕！比罗德岛上的那几只大菲林还要可怕！","id":256,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"至少他没有表露出很强的攻击性。但如果他确实有一整支小队的话......现在的沃伦姆德毫无还手之力。","id":258,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_367_swllow_1","focus":"1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"就这么让他走？","id":260,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_367_swllow_1","focus":"2","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"正面冲突不是好选择，过度刺激对方会让沃伦姆德陷入困境。而且现在还确认不了安托的下落......","id":262,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_367_swllow_1","focus":"1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"......如果连整合运动都出现在这里，事情就麻烦多了。","id":264,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"有联系上亚叶干员和铃兰干员吗？","id":265,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_367_swllow_1","focus":"2","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......不，城内太混乱了，我甚至犹豫是否该以罗德岛的官方身份去拜访议事厅。","id":267,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"不过我也发现了一些让人在意的事情，这似乎并不是常见的感染者冲突。","id":268,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_367_swllow_1","focus":"1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"的确，莱塔尼亚对待感染者向来温和，如果没有其他因素，事情不至于走到这一步。","id":270,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"“冬灵”是个重要的线索，我们可能得继续调查下去。断崖和我走，卡达，麻烦你侦查一下他们的驻扎地点。","id":272,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"我们要掌握他们的队伍规模，以及他们的行动模式，只用看一眼就好，小心为上。","id":273,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"明白！","id":275,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"character","name":"char_294_ayer","name2":"char_367_swllow_1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"断崖","text":"......唉，早知道这样还不如陪莱恩哈特在宿舍里玩石头......","id":277,"figure":"char_294_ayer"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":278},{"type":"dialog","id":279},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"character","id":281},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":282},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"text","text":"哼哼——♪哼哼哼——♪","id":285},{"type":"text","text":"冬灵啊，冬灵♪","id":286},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_ltstreet1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":289},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":291,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"冬灵？你们从哪儿听说这个词的？","id":293,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"dialog","id":294},{"type":"character","id":295},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_ltstreet1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":297},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"你们是什么人？罗德岛？外来者不要掺和那么多，这不关你们什么事。","id":300,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialog","id":301},{"type":"character","id":302},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_ltalley.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"——我不知道什么冬灵，不要和我搭话。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"character","id":309},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":310},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_ltalley.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":311},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"冬灵？调查？不，沃伦姆德早就没有冬灵人了。","id":314,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......早就没有？","id":316,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"不，我的意思是......唉，我就不该理你们。","id":318,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"听着，我不管你们想干什么，但是沃伦姆德是个比你们想象中还要团结的城镇。","id":319,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"也许大部分人连这个规矩都不会告诉你们，但我可以破例给你们解释——","id":320,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"“冬灵人”是沃伦姆德历史的一部分，但这个话题会激起不必要的争端。","id":321,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"在我看来，现在已经因为“冬灵人”引起了相当麻烦的争端了。","id":323,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......你是说前天动力炉被毁的事情？比起这个......","id":325,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"即使这会让沃伦姆德在深冬停滞在这片荒凉的土地上？","id":327,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"天灾让沃伦姆德损失很多，这个冬天不会好过。","id":328,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......外来者，不要得寸进尺。这个话题是贵族老爷们最忌讳提起的事情，我不想找麻烦。","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"如果你真的想知道冬灵人是什么，就去自己问问冬灵人。","id":331,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"诶......不知道冬灵是什么的话要怎么找到冬灵......不讲理嘛......","id":333,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"——够了！","id":335,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"你们自己想办法吧，我不知道，我什么都不知道。","id":336,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialog","id":337},{"type":"character","id":338},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.4","id":339},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"啊......","id":341,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"走掉了......真是过分的人！","id":343,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......团结的城镇？可真是团结。","id":345,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"也许我们还是该去问问塞弗林长官......？","id":347,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯，这是重要的突破口，希望他不要像上次那样逃避话题。","id":349,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但是太阳已经要下山了......","id":350,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......嘁。","id":351,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"*乌萨斯粗口*！为什么今天也一无所获——！","id":352,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐，不要着急......","id":354,"figure":["char_358_lisa_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我没有......！我只是，我......","id":356,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......这里有什么不对劲......我知道的......但是安托她......我到底要怎么办......","id":357,"figure":["char_345_folnic_1",2]},{"type":"character","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......要怎么办，妈妈......","id":359},{"type":"dialog","id":360},{"type":"character","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":362},{"type":"text","text":"哼哼——♪哼哼哼——♪","id":363},{"type":"text","text":"那是一节易折的树枝♪","id":364},{"type":"text","text":"冬灵啊，冬灵♪","id":365},{"type":"text","text":"倦于长久的生和长久的死♪","id":366},{"type":"text","text":"它顽强坚韧地唱它的歌♪","id":367},{"type":"text","text":"唱了一个夏天♪","id":368},{"type":"text","text":"一个冬天之久♪","id":369},{"type":"text","text":"冬灵啊，冬灵♪","id":370},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":371},{"type":"dialog","id":372},{"type":"character","id":373},{"type":"image","id":374}],"characters":["亚叶","铃兰","泥岩","卡达","断崖","灰喉","镇民"]}